org.fcrepo.server.journal.recoverylog

Class RenamingJournalRecoveryLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fcrepo.server.journal.recoverylog.JournalRecoveryLog
      • org.fcrepo.server.journal.recoverylog.RenamingJournalRecoveryLog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JournalConstants

    public class RenamingJournalRecoveryLog
extends JournalRecoveryLog
    A production-oriented implementation of JournalRecoveryLog.

    The name of the log file contains a time-stamp, so we can be sure that it won't over-write an existing log file. Also, the name is prefixed with an '_' (underscore) while the recovery is in progress, so we can see when it finishes.

    Author:
    Jim Blake
